name: Upload
plot: A man is able to choose his own afterlife after his untimely death, by having his consciousness uploaded into a virtual world. As he gets used to his new life and befriends his angel (real world handler), questions about his death arise.

name: Superstore
plot: A look at the lives of employees at a big box store.

name: Fresh of The Boat
plot: Loosely based on the life of Eddie Huang during the mid-to-late 1990s, an Asian-American family decides to move to Orlando, Florida from Washington D.C. in order to embrace the "American Dream," facing many obstacles as they try to assimilate with the new culture that surrounds them.

name: Tacoma FD
plot: Comedic look at firefighters battling their own boredom.
